        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 7. Abdomen and oviscapes of Hypocerides specimens. A–E, Abdomen (white points, tergite margins; gray points, doubtful tergite margins). A, H. sp. from Paraná (Brazil). B, H. sp. from Santa Catarina (Brazil). C, H. sp. from Costa Rica. D, H. sp. from Madagascar. E, H. sp. from USA. F–K Oviscapes. F–G, H. sp. from Santa Catarina (Brazil) (black points, anterior reentrance on ventral margin of segment 8). H–I, H. sp. from Costa Rica. J–K, H. sp. from Madagascar." ;
